# Xcode overwrites the embedded HermesKit package's resolved file with the app's
# full dependency graph (e.g. a stray Sparkle pin HermesKit doesn't depend on).
# The authoritative lock is the app workspace's Package.resolved; this derived
# inner file only churns, so don't track it.
HermesKit/Package.resolved

# Talaria.xcodeproj is generated by XcodeGen from project.yml (the source of
# truth) — run `xcodegen generate` after cloning or after changing source
# membership. Tracking the generated project made project.pbxproj a constant
# cross-branch merge-conflict point. The hand-maintained top-level
# Talaria.xcworkspace stays tracked; only the generated project is ignored.
Talaria.xcodeproj/
